videos.description: ASU running back Eno Benjamin follows his blocks for the 6-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: ASU powers into the end zone

videos.description: Arizona State star wide out N'Keal Harry shakes the cornerback and catches the easy 3-yard TD.
videos.headline: N'Keal Harry shakes defender for TD catch

videos.description: Utah running back Zack Moss catches a high snap and shows off the strength for a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Utah RB takes snap and powers into end zone

videos.description: Utah wide receiver Samson Nacua grabs the touchdown pass from Tyler Huntley giving Utah the lead.
videos.headline: Utah WR hauls in 5-yard TD

videos.description: N'Keal Harry is putting on a show and hauls in a 23-yard touchdown for his second of the day.
videos.headline: Harry hauls in 2nd TD of the day

videos.description: Manny Wilkins throws a strike over the middle to N'Keal Harry, who outruns the defense and reaches for the goal line to make it 28-20 Arizona State.
videos.headline: Harry goes 61 yards for 3rd TD of game

videos.description: Britain Covey can't handle the punt, and Chase Lucas tracks it down to set up another Sun Devils' touchdown drive.
videos.headline: ASU recovers muffed punt

videos.description: RB Eno Benjamin breaks loose and races into the end zone to give Arizona State a 38-20 lead over Utah with under 5 minutes to play.
videos.headline: Benjamin ices game with 44-yard TD run

videos.description: Utah QB Jason Shelley puts a pass up for grabs in the end zone, but Kobe Williams steals it away from Samson Nacua to give the ball back to Arizona State.
videos.headline: ASU's Williams wrestles INT away from Nacua
